@page "/"

<PageTitle>CloudMaps — Overview</PageTitle>

<div class="page-header">
    <h1>CloudMaps Component Demo</h1>
    <p>
        Comprehensive showcase of the Azure Maps Blazor component with advanced features including
        pin management, zone overlays, reverse geocoding with Cloud Geography subdivisions, live
        tracking, and historical position replay.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">Getting Started</h2>
    <p class="card-subtitle">
        Before running the demos, ensure you have:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Azure Maps Subscription Key:</strong> Set it in the application configuration or appsettings.json</li>
        <li><strong>Browser Location Permission:</strong> The "Locate Me" button and auto-locate features require geolocation access</li>
        <li><strong>Map Interaction:</strong> Double-click to add markers, drag markers to update coordinates, double-click markers to remove</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">Feature Demonstrations</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📍 Basic Markers</h3>
            <p>
                Add pins to the map by double-clicking, drag them to update coordinates, and remove
                them by double-clicking. View current latitude/longitude values for each marker.
            </p>
            <NavLink href="basic-markers" class="feature-link">Explore →</NavLink>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🏙️ Reverse Geocoding</h3>
            <p>
                Drag the center pin on the map to get the address via Azure Maps Reverse Geocoding.
                Integration with Cloud Geography shows country and administrative subdivisions.
            </p>
            <NavLink href="reverse-geocode" class="feature-link">Explore →</NavLink>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🗺️ Regions & Zones</h3>
            <p>
                Display administrative boundaries as colored region overlays. Each region has a label
                and visual distinction. Legend shows all displayed regions.
            </p>
            <NavLink href="regions" class="feature-link">Explore →</NavLink>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📡 Live Tracking</h3>
            <p>
                Real-time position updates for single or multiple tracked items. Watch markers move
                as new positions arrive, simulating GPS tracking scenarios.
            </p>
            <NavLink href="live-tracking" class="feature-link">Explore →</NavLink>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📹 History Replay</h3>
            <p>
                Load a historical GPS trace and replay it with speed control. Watch the journey unfold
                with proper timeline visualization and position history polyline.
            </p>
            <NavLink href="history-tracking" class="feature-link">Explore →</NavLink>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>⚙️ Controls & Styles</h3>
            <p>
                Explore all available map controls and styles. Toggle zoom, compass, pitch, style picker,
                fullscreen, and scale controls. Switch between satellite, road, grayscale, and night styles.
            </p>
            <NavLink href="controls-styles" class="feature-link">Explore →</NavLink>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .feature-card {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 16px;
        transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #0078d4;
    }

    .feature-card p {
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #666;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .feature-link {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        background: #0078d4;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .feature-link:hover {
        background: #106ebe;
    }
</style>
